\c 38
\s Ukugula kukaHezekhiya
\p
\v 1 Ngalezonsuku uHezekhiya wagula waphos'ukufa\x + 33.24. 38.8. 2 Kho. 20.1-6. 20.9-11. 2 Lan. 32.24.\x*. UIsaya indodana kaAmozi umprofethi\x + 1.1.\x* wasefika kuye, wathi kuye: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Layezela indlu yakho, ngoba uzakufa, kawuyikuphila.
\v 2 UHezekhiya wasephendulela ubuso bakhe ngasemdulini, wakhuleka eN\nd kosi\nd*ni,
\v 3 wathi: Ngiyakuncenga, N\nd kosi\nd*, ake ukhumbule ukuthi ngihambe phambi kwakho ngobuqotho langenhliziyo epheleleyo, ngenza okulungileyo emehlweni akho. UHezekhiya wasekhala inyembezi ngokukhala okukhulu.
\p
\v 4 Kwasekufika ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* kuIsaya, lisithi:
\v 5 Hamba, uthi kuHezekhiya: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu kaDavida uyihlo: Ngiwuzwile umkhuleko wakho, ngibonile inyembezi zakho; khangela, ngizakwengezelela iminyaka elitshumi lanhlanu ensukwini zakho,
\v 6 ngikukhulule wena lalumuzi esandleni senkosi yeAsiriya, ngiwuvikele lumuzi\x + 37.35.\x*.
\v 7 Lalesi yisibonakaliso kuwe esivela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, esokuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* izayenza le into eyikhulumileyo.
\v 8 Khangela, ngizabuyisela emuva isithunzi sezinyathelo\x + 2 Kho. 20.9,10.\x* esesehlile ezinyathelweni zelanga zikaAhazi, izinyathelo ezilitshumi emuva. Ilanga laselibuyela emuva izinyathelo ezilitshumi, ngezinyathelo elalehle ngazo.
\p
\v 9 Umbhalo kaHezekhiya inkosi yakoJuda lapho egula, esesile emkhuhlaneni wakhe.
\p
\v 10 Mina ngathi: Ekuqunyweni kwezinsuku zami\x + Hlab. 102.24.\x* ngizakuya emasangweni engcwaba\x + Mat. 16.18. Jobe 38.17.\x*; ngemukiwe insali yeminyaka yami.
\v 11 Ngathi: Kangiyikubona uJehova\x + Hlab. 68.4.\x*, uJehova\x + Hlab. 68.4.\x* elizweni labaphilayo\x + Hlab. 27.13.\x*; kangisayikubona muntu labahlali bomhlaba.
\v 12 Isizukulwana sami sesisukile, sasuswa kimi njengethente lomelusi\x + 2 Kor. 5.1.\x*; ngiqume impilo yami njengomeluki\x + Jobe 7.6.\x*; uzangiquma\x + Jobe 6.9.\x* njengomkhuhlane ocikizayo\f + \fk njengomkhuhlane ocikizayo: \fl Heb. \fq eselukweni.\f*; kusukela emini kuze kube sebusuku uzangiqeda\x + Jobe 4.20.\x*.
\v 13 Ngabalisa kwaze kwaba sekuseni\x + Jobe 4.20.\x*; njengesilwane\x + Jobe 10.16.\x*, ngokunjalo uzakwephula amathambo ami wonke; kusukela emini kuze kube sebusuku uzangiqeda\x + Jobe 4.20.\x*.
\v 14 Njengenkonjane\x + Jer. 8.7.\x* \add kumbe\add* ihemu\x + Jer. 8.7.\x*, ngokunjalo ngatshiyoza\x + 8.19.\x*; ngilila njengejuba\x + 8.19.\x*\x + 59.11. Hez. 7.16.\x*; amehlo ami afiphala \add ngokukhangela\add* phezulu\x + Hlab. 69.3.\x*. Nkosi, ngicindezelwe; woba yisibambiso sami\x + Jobe 17.3.\x*.
\v 15 Ngingathini? Ikhulumile kimi, yona uqobo ikwenzile. Ngizahamba kabuthakathaka\x + Hlab. 42.4. 1 Kho. 21.27.\x* yonke iminyaka yami ebuhlungwini bomphefumulo wami\x + Jobe 7.11.\x*.
\v 16 Nkosi, ngalezizinto bayaphila\x + Hlab. 119.25,37. Hlab. 119.71,75.\x*, lakuzo zonke lezizinto kulempilo yomoya wami. Njalo uzangelapha, ungiphilise\x + Hlab. 119.25,37. Hlab. 119.71,75.\x*.
\v 17 Khangela, kulokuthula ngibe lobuhlungu obukhulu, kodwa wena uwuthandile umphefumulo wami \add wawukhulula\add* egodini lencithakalo, ngoba uphosele ngemva komhlana wakho zonke izono zami\x + 33.24. Mika 7.19. Hlab. 103.12.\x*\x + Hos. 7.2.\x*.
\v 18 Ngoba ingcwaba lingekubonge\x + Hlab. 6.5. Tshu. 9.10.\x*; ukufa ku\add nge\add*kudumise; labo abehlela emgodini\x + 14.19. Hlab. 28. 1.\x* bangelithembele iqiniso lakho.
\v 19 Ophilayo, ophilayo, yena uzakudumisa, njengami lamuhla; uyise uzakwazisa abantwana iqiniso lakho\x + Dute. 4.9. 6.7. Hlab. 78.3,4. 145.4.\x*.
\v 20 IN\nd kosi\nd* \add yayilungele\add* ukungisindisa; ngakho sizahlabelela izingoma zami ngamachacho\x + Hab. 3.19. Jobe 30.9. Hlab. 150.4.\x* insuku zonke zempilo yethu endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*.
\p
\v 21 Ngoba uIsaya\x + 2 Kho. 20.7.\x* wayethe: Kabathathe isigaqa somkhiwa, basifake njengomnameko phezu kwethumba, njalo uzasila.
\v 22 UHezekhiya\x + 2 Kho. 20.8.\x* laye wayethe: Siyini isibonakaliso sokuthi ngizakwenyukela endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 2 Kho. 20.5.\x*?